article.description: — Trent Buttrick had 16 points, seven rebounds and five steals as UMass topped UMBC 77-60 on Tuesday night in a season opener.
article.headline: Buttrick, Weeks score 16 each to carry UMass over UMBC 77-60
article.linkText: Buttrick, Weeks score 16 each to carry UMass over UMBC 77-60
article.story: AMHERST, Mass. -- — Trent Buttrick had 16 points, seven rebounds and five steals as UMass topped UMBC 77-60 on Tuesday night in a season opener. T.J. Weeks Jr. had 16 points and seven rebounds for UMass. Noah Fernandes added 12 points. Rich Kelly had six assists. Keondre Kennedy had 13 points and eight rebounds for the Retrievers. Dimitrije Spasojevic added 10 points and nine rebounds. L.J. Owens had 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
